  "content": "<div class=\"css-376mun\"><span id=\"content\"><span class=\"RichText ztext CopyrightRichText-richText css-10o75c2\" options=\"[object Object]\" itemprop=\"text\"><h3 data-first-child=\"\">新郎去医院做婚检，本来是想让医院肯定自己的身体状况，谁知道医院却否定了自己的性别。</h3><p data-pid=\"B4qTw7sX\">杭州的沈先生去杭州市临平区妇幼保健院做婚检，谁知拿回来的检验报告单显示，沈先生从生理角度上讲是女性。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-68c28865aa363fdedad07e7acae069f2_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"663\" data-original-token=\"v2-09c30aaa136fb763667a18030318b924\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ef929314e3ac818780d16c401fdd6968_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-68c28865aa363fdedad07e7acae069f2_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-68c28865aa363fdedad07e7acae069f2_720w.webp?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1080\" data-rawheight=\"663\" data-original-token=\"v2-09c30aaa136fb763667a18030318b924\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-ef929314e3ac818780d16c401fdd6968_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1080\" data-original=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-68c28865aa363fdedad07e7acae069f2_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-68c28865aa363fdedad07e7acae069f2_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" height=\"663\" data-lazy-status=\"ok\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"a3HGlXmF\">这事让哪个大老爷们遇到都会相当的震惊，当男人二三十年，没想到临近结婚时，性别还被否定了。</p><p data-pid=\"-RxuKwC-\">沈先生表示怀疑，去医院再次确认。</p><p data-pid=\"ny9wPsPH\">医生信誓旦旦的回复，<span><a class=\"RichContent-EntityWord css-b7erz1\" data-za-not-track-link=\"true\" data-paste-text=\"true\" href=\"https://zhida.zhihu.com/search?content_id=474458240&amp;content_type=Answer&amp;match_order=1&amp;q=%E6%9F%93%E8%89%B2%E4%BD%93&amp;zhida_source=entity\" target=\"_blank\">染色体<svg width=\"10px\" height=\"10px\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" class=\"ZDI ZDI--FourPointedStar16 css-1dvsrp\" fill=\"currentColor\"><path d=\"m5.068 9.267-3.08-.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0-.994l3.08-.77a2.289 2.289 0 0 0 1.665-1.665l.77-3.08a.512.512 0 0 1 .994 0l.77 3.08c.205.82.845 1.46 1.665 1.665l3.08.77a.512.512 0 0 1 0 .994l-3.08.77a2.29 2.29 0 0 0-1.665 1.665l-.77 3.08a.512.512 0 0 1-.994 0l-.77-3.08a2.289 2.289 0 0 0-1.665-1.665Z\"></path></svg></a></span>的报告错误率是很低的，意思就是不会出问题。</p><p data-pid=\"d8ixpud1\">沈先生那时情绪也是相当低落，睡不好觉，也不知如何面对妻子，期间还产生了与妻子分开的念头。</p><p data-pid=\"hAxKZ7aO\">谁知没几天，医院又说由于他们的失误，检测报告搞错了。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-91d1c059b4d6293973a0478d3c765092_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"500\" data-original-token=\"v2-a2738e29771ef7ac1440a020507c14e1\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8d003f4fb9a004fb6ca7c7b794bcb5f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-91d1c059b4d6293973a0478d3c765092_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='500' height='500'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"500\" data-rawheight=\"500\" data-original-token=\"v2-a2738e29771ef7ac1440a020507c14e1\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d8d003f4fb9a004fb6ca7c7b794bcb5f_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"500\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-91d1c059b4d6293973a0478d3c765092_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-91d1c059b4d6293973a0478d3c765092_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p data-pid=\"igQfn2Qn\">医生先以检测报告是第三方出的，把责任推卸干净，然后才是道歉，承认工作疏忽。</p><p data-pid=\"tTxa0-4A\">听起来也太儿戏了，男人最大的奇耻大辱就是被说不是男人，这家婚检中心简直做的太绝了。</p><p data-pid=\"_pFCzPI4\">那个第三方机构也是个大水货，整套流程下来需要三个人签字，结果没有一个人发现这么大的bug，那假如真有什么隐秘点的问题，还指望着他们发现出来吗？</p><p data-pid=\"1tro29jr\">与其说是婚检，不如说是走过场，真有问题的话，真检查不出来啊，还平白无故的来点惊吓。</p><p data-pid=\"QXyE2dGZ\">沈先生说的很对，这家医院和那个机构存在很大的漏洞，工作流程和管理方面都有大问题。</p><p data-pid=\"8W-d49pN\">幸好问题及时发现并且改正过来，否则沈先生的这辈子的幸福，就葬送在这家不负责任的医院和第三方机构手里，那将是一个多么大的悲剧。</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7e10775afe89a6c7df4fb75e768a3b8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"638\" data-rawheight=\"451\" data-original-token=\"v2-4711f667cc58fd88ba88d5ccaef78ab4\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-03b86ce701551a56612d84cdb6f33914_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"638\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e7e10775afe89a6c7df4fb75e768a3b8_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\"/></noscript><div><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,<svg xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' width='638' height='451'></svg>\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"638\" data-rawheight=\"451\" data-original-token=\"v2-4711f667cc58fd88ba88d5ccaef78ab4\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-03b86ce701551a56612d84cdb6f33914_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"638\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-e7e10775afe89a6c7df4fb75e768a3b8_r.jpg?source=1def8aca\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-e7e10775afe89a6c7df4fb75e768a3b8_720w.jpg?source=1def8aca\"></div></figure><p></p></span><span id=\"VirtualCatalogAnchorPoint\"></span></span></div>",
